    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK562">
<l>kaṭitōcci mella veṟika neṭitākka </l>
<l> nīṅkāmai vēṇṭu pavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let the king, who desires that his prosperity may long remain, commence his preliminary enquires with strictness, and then punish with mildness.</l>
            </lg>
